===Judicial appointments===
[[File:Thomas Stanley Matthews - Brady-Handy.jpg|thumb|alt=Black and white photo of a man with a full beard in a three piece suit|[[Stanley Matthews (lawyer)|Stanley Matthews]], appointed to the Supreme Court by Garfield in 1881]]
Despite his short tenure in office, Garfield was able to appoint a Justice to the [[Supreme Court of the United States]] and four other federal judges.

